        <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>In this new historical investigation, German historian Jens Weste-meier portrays the rise and fall of an SS war criminal, and demolishes persistent myths of a Nazi icon. The picture revealed here is at odds with the popular Peiper mythology created by wartime and contemporary National Socialist propaganda, novels, motion pictures, and right-wing Peiper biographies. Using primar...</p><p><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="j a_show_full">(å±•å¼€å…¨éƒ¨)</a></p></div>
